1
00:01:31,940 --> 00:01:32,979
Mrs. He.

2
00:01:33,380 --> 00:01:34,380
Everyone's expecting you.
Please hurry.

3
00:01:35,259 --> 00:01:36,020
-Coming.
-I...

4
00:01:38,259 --> 00:01:39,940
I'll give it a shot, then.

5
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:41,139
Go on.

6
00:01:41,339 --> 00:01:42,300
For your sake,

7
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:43,740
I'll add another 100 taels.

8
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:54,059
Any lord here

9
00:01:54,460 --> 00:01:56,300
care to give it a try?

10
00:02:24,059 --> 00:02:25,180
Well, then,

11
00:02:25,740 --> 00:02:27,619
I suppose I'll have a go.

12
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:50,180
Lord Chen hit all five.

13
00:02:50,379 --> 00:02:52,219
Mrs. He got two out of five.

14
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:54,539
Lord Chen wins.

15
00:02:55,499 --> 00:02:56,700
The prize is now

16
00:02:56,939 --> 00:02:58,180
1,000 taels.

17
00:03:10,740 --> 00:03:12,180
Wenxiu is up!

18
00:03:19,300 --> 00:03:19,860
Yanying.

19
00:03:21,020 --> 00:03:22,260
Where did your brother

20
00:03:22,619 --> 00:03:23,619
learn archery?

21
00:03:24,339 --> 00:03:25,059
When he was little,

22
00:03:25,059 --> 00:03:26,539
he learned from our guards.

23
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:28,059
But he probably got this good

24
00:03:28,059 --> 00:03:28,980
after joining the yamen.

25
00:03:42,180 --> 00:03:44,219
Lord Chen hit all five.

26
00:03:45,260 --> 00:03:47,740
Mr. Yao got three out of five.

27
00:03:48,379 --> 00:03:49,619
The prize money is now

28
00:03:50,020 --> 00:03:51,819
1,500 taels.

29
00:03:52,659 --> 00:03:54,140
That's another win.

30
00:03:56,020 --> 00:03:57,219
Yanying, you're up.

31
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:32,539
Lord Chen wins again.

32
00:04:33,179 --> 00:04:34,339
The prize is now

33
00:04:34,580 --> 00:04:36,020
2,000 taels.

34
00:04:38,339 --> 00:04:38,779
Hyah!

35
00:04:44,620 --> 00:04:45,900
Didn't you say you'd win?

36
00:04:46,099 --> 00:04:47,659
He usually goes easy on me.

37
00:04:47,940 --> 00:04:49,339
Why not today?

38
00:04:51,140 --> 00:04:52,299
Watch me end his streak.

39
00:05:11,460 --> 00:05:11,979
Miss Xue,
after you.

40
00:05:13,020 --> 00:05:13,419
After you.

41
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:15,940
Hyah!

42
00:05:27,820 --> 00:05:28,179
Hyah!

43
00:05:34,739 --> 00:05:35,500
Missed?

44
00:05:35,940 --> 00:05:37,060
No way.

45
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:52,700
What's my brother doing?

46
00:05:56,779 --> 00:05:58,500
Why is Jiuheng messing up?

47
00:06:08,020 --> 00:06:10,179
Lord Chen hit the center twice

48
00:06:10,580 --> 00:06:11,900
and missed the other three.

49
00:06:12,859 --> 00:06:15,580
Miss Xue hit all five.

50
00:06:16,060 --> 00:06:16,739
Round one,

51
00:06:17,020 --> 00:06:18,779
-Hyah!
-Miss Xue won.

52
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:20,900
What's gotten into him?

53
00:06:21,580 --> 00:06:22,979
He's obviously doing it on purpose

54
00:06:23,339 --> 00:06:24,339
to let Miss Xue win.

55
00:06:24,659 --> 00:06:26,140
But I told him

56
00:06:26,260 --> 00:06:27,940
Qinglan hates being handed a win.

57
00:06:28,380 --> 00:06:28,940
What?

58
00:06:29,580 --> 00:06:30,539
You told him that?
Yes.

59
00:06:33,339 --> 00:06:34,539
Did he do it on purpose?

60
00:06:36,179 --> 00:06:37,940
Qinglan must be furious.

61
00:07:02,779 --> 00:07:04,020
Why did Miss Xue stop?

62
00:07:06,299 --> 00:07:07,500
How did you miss again?

63
00:07:08,419 --> 00:07:09,779
I'm out of practice.

64
00:07:09,940 --> 00:07:11,339
After so many rounds,

65
00:07:11,820 --> 00:07:12,700
my arms are giving out.

66
00:07:20,179 --> 00:07:20,739
I'm done.

67
00:07:21,060 --> 00:07:21,779
I give up.

68
00:07:32,859 --> 00:07:34,299
Why go that far, Miss Xue?

69
00:07:35,140 --> 00:07:36,539
You clearly let me win.

70
00:07:37,140 --> 00:07:38,060
If you let me win,
you don't respect me.

71
00:07:39,539 --> 00:07:40,260
If you don't respect me,
what's there to compete for?

72
00:07:42,460 --> 00:07:43,020
I'm done.
Hyah!

73
00:07:47,779 --> 00:07:50,099
Qinglan really has a temper.

74
00:07:50,380 --> 00:07:51,979
I fear Jiuheng

75
00:07:52,179 --> 00:07:53,299
has a rough road ahead.

76
00:07:54,460 --> 00:07:55,179
This girl...

77
00:07:55,739 --> 00:07:56,659
Jiuheng let her win.
Why is she still angry?

78
00:07:59,460 --> 00:08:00,099
My lord.

79
00:08:00,339 --> 00:08:01,140
Don't be upset.

80
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:02,779
I'll talk to her later.

81
00:08:06,419 --> 00:08:07,140
No need.

82
00:08:08,620 --> 00:08:09,900
If it isn't meant to be,

83
00:08:11,179 --> 00:08:12,260
we shouldn't force it.

84
00:08:25,900 --> 00:08:26,979
Your brother let me win on purpose.

85
00:08:27,260 --> 00:08:27,979
That's no fun.

86
00:08:28,339 --> 00:08:29,539
Qinglan, don't be angry.

87
00:08:29,620 --> 00:08:30,979
My brother is always so proper.

88
00:08:31,099 --> 00:08:31,539
So he may have...
Of course you'd defend him.

89
00:08:35,579 --> 00:08:36,179
Forget it.

90
00:08:37,260 --> 00:08:38,100
I don't want to talk about it.

91
00:08:39,539 --> 00:08:40,220
I just can't stand

92
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:41,419
the way he acts so full of himself.

93
00:08:41,819 --> 00:08:42,740
It gets on my nerves.

94
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:50,140
I'll do it.

95
00:08:51,939 --> 00:08:52,500
Really?

96
00:08:53,900 --> 00:08:54,900
All right, then.

97
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:56,620
If you can win,

98
00:08:56,900 --> 00:08:58,340
I'll add 500 taels to the prize.

99
00:08:59,260 --> 00:09:01,020
Then get your silver ready.

100
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:01,659
Deal.

101
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:11,500
This Miss Gu...

102
00:09:11,740 --> 00:09:12,779
She's really something.

103
00:09:20,020 --> 00:09:21,020
I didn't know Miss Xue
was so special

104
00:09:22,220 --> 00:09:23,020
in your eyes.

105
00:09:23,459 --> 00:09:24,419
I've never seen you

106
00:09:24,620 --> 00:09:25,539
go that easy on anyone.

107
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:28,620
I thought you might sit this out.

108
00:09:30,179 --> 00:09:30,740
What?

109
00:09:31,140 --> 00:09:32,100
You want to go easy on me too?

110
00:09:33,939 --> 00:09:35,059
You're one of us.

111
00:09:35,939 --> 00:09:36,939
No need to hold back.

112
00:09:48,539 --> 00:09:49,179
Yanying.

113
00:09:49,659 --> 00:09:50,419
Come sit here.
You'll get a better view.

114
00:09:51,299 --> 00:09:52,140
Okay.

115
00:09:55,299 --> 00:09:55,699
Hyah!

116
00:10:14,939 --> 00:10:17,299
Lord Chen hit all five arrows.

117
00:10:17,939 --> 00:10:20,340
Miss Gu hit all five shots.

118
00:10:20,980 --> 00:10:21,860
Round one.

119
00:10:22,459 --> 00:10:23,059
It's a tie.

120
00:10:24,939 --> 00:10:25,699
Not bad.

121
00:10:26,740 --> 00:10:27,539
What's that girl's name?

122
00:10:28,299 --> 00:10:28,980
My lord,

123
00:10:29,140 --> 00:10:30,100
that's Chen Yanyun.

124
00:10:33,260 --> 00:10:34,539
Of course I know Chen Yanyun.

125
00:10:35,059 --> 00:10:36,059
I'm asking about the girl.

126
00:10:36,539 --> 00:10:37,380
Go find out for me.

127
00:10:38,299 --> 00:10:39,299
Get me a clear answer,

128
00:10:40,220 --> 00:10:40,819
and you'll be rewarded.

129
00:10:41,819 --> 00:10:42,500
No problem.

130
00:10:47,819 --> 00:10:48,900
Nice shot.

131
00:10:50,419 --> 00:10:51,179
I did all right.

132
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:53,260
My teacher wanted me

133
00:10:53,260 --> 00:10:54,620
to be matched with Miss Xue.

134
00:10:55,380 --> 00:10:56,500
I couldn't turn him down outright.

135
00:10:57,179 --> 00:10:58,419
So I had to take

136
00:10:58,419 --> 00:10:59,260
a more roundabout way.

137
00:10:59,699 --> 00:11:00,459
But don't worry.

138
00:11:01,340 --> 00:11:02,179
She and I

139
00:11:02,779 --> 00:11:03,459
will never happen.

140
00:11:06,980 --> 00:11:08,980
You're trying to throw me off.

141
00:11:12,220 --> 00:11:12,659
Hyah!

142
00:11:13,779 --> 00:11:14,740
Be careful.

143
00:11:21,980 --> 00:11:23,020
Round two.

144
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:51,620
Lord Chen hit all five arrows.

145
00:11:52,020 --> 00:11:54,659
Miss Gu hit all five shots.

146
00:11:55,380 --> 00:11:56,459
Round two.

147
00:11:57,340 --> 00:11:57,980
A tie.

148
00:11:58,220 --> 00:11:59,620
Two ties in a row.

149
00:11:59,980 --> 00:12:01,659
We actually get a third round.

150
00:12:03,299 --> 00:12:03,939
Ruixiang.

151
00:12:05,539 --> 00:12:06,980
Add another 100 taels to the prize.

152
00:12:07,579 --> 00:12:08,340
Call it out loud.
Get everyone else going.

153
00:12:09,980 --> 00:12:10,579
Okay.

154
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:12,260
I'll add 100 taels too.

155
00:12:15,779 --> 00:12:19,179
Miss Xue adds 100 taels.

156
00:12:19,380 --> 00:12:22,579
Miss Chen adds 100 taels.

157
00:12:23,220 --> 00:12:25,140
Mrs. Fu adds

158
00:12:25,939 --> 00:12:27,260
200 taels.

159
00:12:27,579 --> 00:12:29,380
Mrs. Wang adds

160
00:12:29,980 --> 00:12:31,539
100 taels.

161
00:12:31,900 --> 00:12:33,860
Mrs. He adds...

162
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:34,900
How did you make that horse
-come to me?
-100 taels.

163
00:12:36,900 --> 00:12:38,220
You always wear osmanthus scent.

164
00:12:38,699 --> 00:12:40,140
After we got back from Tongzhou,

165
00:12:40,459 --> 00:12:41,100
I had the groom

166
00:12:41,100 --> 00:12:42,419
who looks after Yuhua

167
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:44,220
scent his clothes

168
00:12:44,459 --> 00:12:45,260
with osmanthus every day.

169
00:12:46,059 --> 00:12:46,939
The horse is clever.

170
00:12:47,380 --> 00:12:48,179
It didn't let me down.

171
00:12:51,100 --> 00:12:52,260
You really thought this through.

172
00:12:56,659 --> 00:12:57,819
Later,

173
00:12:58,900 --> 00:13:00,500
did you think it over?

174
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:05,579
I did.

175
00:13:06,620 --> 00:13:07,620
If someone else married you,

176
00:13:08,140 --> 00:13:09,340
she'd become Mrs. Ge.

177
00:13:10,020 --> 00:13:11,419
She'd gain wealth and status.

178
00:13:12,140 --> 00:13:12,939
But I'm different.

179
00:13:13,299 --> 00:13:14,299
I don't need money.

180
00:13:14,860 --> 00:13:15,620
And I don't want

181
00:13:15,620 --> 00:13:17,980
to marry for wealth or rank.

182
00:13:18,939 --> 00:13:20,260
Once I become a titled lady,

183
00:13:20,459 --> 00:13:21,380
everything I do

184
00:13:21,819 --> 00:13:22,900
will be judged by others.

185
00:13:23,459 --> 00:13:24,419
The rules for women,

186
00:13:24,419 --> 00:13:25,500
I'll have to follow them all.

187
00:13:27,380 --> 00:13:28,539
So I thought about it for a long time.

188
00:13:28,699 --> 00:13:29,620
But I still can't see

189
00:13:30,140 --> 00:13:30,819
how marrying you

190
00:13:31,020 --> 00:13:32,419
would do me any good.

191
00:13:33,819 --> 00:13:34,579
And it's the same for you.

192
00:13:35,140 --> 00:13:35,860
If you marry me,

193
00:13:36,179 --> 00:13:37,419
what good would it do you?

194
00:13:37,939 --> 00:13:39,020
That's not quite true.

195
00:13:39,620 --> 00:13:40,260
Maybe

196
00:13:40,819 --> 00:13:42,579
marrying me won't help you much.

197
00:13:43,179 --> 00:13:44,059
But if I marry you,

198
00:13:44,740 --> 00:13:46,299
it helps me quite a lot.

199
00:13:48,260 --> 00:13:48,939
How so?

200
00:13:49,459 --> 00:13:50,140
Think about it.

201
00:13:51,059 --> 00:13:52,100
Everyone at court knows

202
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:53,380
I'm my teacher's man.

203
00:13:53,860 --> 00:13:54,539
If I marry

204
00:13:54,539 --> 00:13:55,939
the woman he picked for me,

205
00:13:56,659 --> 00:13:57,299
wouldn't that make me

206
00:13:57,299 --> 00:13:58,579
a Fu faction man for sure?

207
00:13:59,819 --> 00:14:00,980
Tied to them for life.

208
00:14:02,539 --> 00:14:03,500
But actually,

209
00:14:04,579 --> 00:14:05,579
I don't want to take sides yet.

210
00:14:08,740 --> 00:14:09,819
You shouldn't say that here.

211
00:14:11,779 --> 00:14:13,299
Don't worry. They can't hear us.

212
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:15,459
The court is shifting.

213
00:14:15,779 --> 00:14:17,220
Everyone is changing, too.

214
00:14:17,779 --> 00:14:18,659
I don't want to

215
00:14:19,059 --> 00:14:21,020
use my marriage

216
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:23,179
and decide where I stand

217
00:14:23,179 --> 00:14:23,860
for the next few decades.

218
00:14:24,539 --> 00:14:25,260
I'd rather

219
00:14:26,100 --> 00:14:28,579
marry someone outside all factions,

220
00:14:29,260 --> 00:14:29,740
someone

221
00:14:29,740 --> 00:14:31,539
I can truly trust.

222
00:14:32,100 --> 00:14:32,860
And as luck would have it,

223
00:14:33,659 --> 00:14:35,459
this woman is also rich.

224
00:14:37,539 --> 00:14:38,179
And just so happens,

225
00:14:41,740 --> 00:14:43,500
I like this woman very much.

226
00:14:46,699 --> 00:14:48,779
That's my good fortune.

227
00:14:50,380 --> 00:14:51,740
You really do flatter yourself.

228
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:57,059
There’s one more thing.

229
00:14:58,140 --> 00:14:58,740
It just so happens

230
00:15:07,260 --> 00:15:08,179
that this woman

231
00:15:10,299 --> 00:15:11,419
likes me, too.

232
00:15:16,620 --> 00:15:18,779
The third round is about to begin.

233
00:15:18,779 --> 00:15:21,140
Lord Chen and Miss Gu,

234
00:15:21,140 --> 00:15:22,539
please come to the field.

235
00:15:30,620 --> 00:15:31,419
My lord,
I found out.

236
00:15:32,340 --> 00:15:33,260
Her name is Gu Jinzhao.

237
00:15:33,500 --> 00:15:35,220
Lord Gu Deyuan's niece.

238
00:15:36,100 --> 00:15:37,419
Jinzhao.

239
00:15:39,340 --> 00:15:40,140
Good.

240
00:15:40,980 --> 00:15:42,020
If she wins,

241
00:15:42,220 --> 00:15:43,260
I'll challenge her myself.

242
00:15:43,579 --> 00:15:44,100
Lord,

243
00:15:44,819 --> 00:15:45,939
what if Miss Gu

244
00:15:45,939 --> 00:15:46,860
loses?

245
00:15:47,220 --> 00:15:48,020
Loses?

246
00:15:48,860 --> 00:15:50,380
Then I'll beat Chen Yanyun

247
00:15:51,779 --> 00:15:52,659
and avenge her.

248
00:15:52,659 --> 00:15:53,980
Brilliant, sir.

249
00:15:56,100 --> 00:15:56,620
Here.

250
00:15:57,620 --> 00:15:59,100
Thank you, sir.

251
00:16:01,340 --> 00:16:02,620
Round three.

252
00:16:02,779 --> 00:16:03,220
Hyah!
Hyah!

253
00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:30,380
Round three,

254
00:16:30,699 --> 00:16:32,100
Miss Gu wins.

255
00:16:32,659 --> 00:16:33,380
This match

256
00:16:33,980 --> 00:16:35,459
goes to Miss Gu.

257
00:16:36,059 --> 00:16:37,419
The prize is now

258
00:16:38,179 --> 00:16:39,620
-4,500 taels.
-Excellent!

259
00:16:39,620 --> 00:16:40,260
Bring the wine.

260
00:16:59,579 --> 00:17:00,100
Nicely done.

261
00:17:02,459 --> 00:17:02,980
Do it.

262
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:03,860
Okay.
Go.

263
00:17:10,780 --> 00:17:11,300
Hyah!

264
00:17:11,540 --> 00:17:14,060
Hyah! Hyah! Hyah!

265
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:16,900
Hyah! Hyah! Hyah!

266
00:17:17,979 --> 00:17:19,259
Hyah! Hyah! Hyah!

267
00:17:20,900 --> 00:17:21,820
Criminal Investigation Bureau on a case!

268
00:17:21,979 --> 00:17:23,019
-Bystanders, move!
-Gu Jinzhao,

269
00:17:23,540 --> 00:17:24,419
I'm coming!

270
00:17:27,459 --> 00:17:29,340
Hyah! Hyah! Hyah!

271
00:17:30,060 --> 00:17:30,459
Hyah!

272
00:17:31,179 --> 00:17:34,100
Hyah! Hyah! Hyah!

273
00:17:36,219 --> 00:17:38,860
Hyah! Hyah! Hyah!

274
00:17:39,820 --> 00:17:40,259
Hyah!

275
00:17:41,820 --> 00:17:43,300
Hyah! Hyah!

276
00:17:52,259 --> 00:17:53,499
We're after a wanted criminal.

277
00:17:53,659 --> 00:17:54,179
Move aside!

278
00:17:54,459 --> 00:17:56,100
The Bureau's men?

279
00:17:56,739 --> 00:17:57,900
What are they doing here?

280
00:18:24,939 --> 00:18:25,459
Seize him.

281
00:18:36,580 --> 00:18:37,060
Ma'am.

282
00:18:38,699 --> 00:18:39,019
Go.
Ma'am.

283
00:18:39,659 --> 00:18:40,179
How dare you!
Go!

284
00:18:40,780 --> 00:18:41,219
Outrageous!

285
00:18:41,219 --> 00:18:42,380
I'm a court official!

286
00:18:42,699 --> 00:18:43,699
A director at the Ministry of Justice!

287
00:18:44,219 --> 00:18:45,259
You Bureau men

288
00:18:45,259 --> 00:18:46,620
dare lay hands on your superior?

289
00:18:47,259 --> 00:18:49,100
I demand to see His Majesty!

290
00:18:49,860 --> 00:18:50,300
Move!

291
00:18:58,580 --> 00:18:58,939
Kneel!

292
00:19:00,780 --> 00:19:01,860
Who did they arrest?

293
00:19:02,419 --> 00:19:03,100
Master Xuan,

294
00:19:03,620 --> 00:19:05,060
Du Wangfa from Justice.

295
00:19:06,340 --> 00:19:07,259
Who's leading them?

296
00:19:07,459 --> 00:19:08,100
Zhang Ling?

297
00:19:08,499 --> 00:19:09,419
Not Commander Zhang.

298
00:19:10,100 --> 00:19:10,620
It's...

299
00:19:11,699 --> 00:19:12,419
Lord Ye.

300
00:20:20,739 --> 00:20:21,179
My lord.
We've got him.

301
00:20:24,060 --> 00:20:24,620
Take him back.
Yes.

302
00:20:26,060 --> 00:20:26,419
Take him away.
Move.

303
00:20:27,580 --> 00:20:28,300
Let go of me!

304
00:20:29,820 --> 00:20:31,100
I'm a court official!

305
00:20:32,140 --> 00:20:32,580
Let go!

306
00:20:34,380 --> 00:20:34,939
Hold it.

307
00:20:41,060 --> 00:20:42,019
Today's spring outing

308
00:20:42,019 --> 00:20:43,259
is full of high officials

309
00:20:43,259 --> 00:20:43,900
and their families.

310
00:20:44,060 --> 00:20:45,219
How dare you cause trouble here?

311
00:20:47,179 --> 00:20:47,739
Who are you?

312
00:20:48,979 --> 00:20:49,739
Xue Qinglan.

313
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:51,300
One of today's hosts.

314
00:20:54,380 --> 00:20:56,100
Then you're hiding a wanted man.

315
00:20:57,979 --> 00:20:59,580
Want a cell at Criminal Investigation Bureau, too?

316
00:20:59,900 --> 00:21:00,499
You wouldn't dare.

317
00:21:01,300 --> 00:21:02,100
Why wouldn't I?

318
00:21:03,019 --> 00:21:03,900
If you have a problem,

319
00:21:04,419 --> 00:21:06,060
tell your father to cry in court.

320
00:21:06,380 --> 00:21:06,780
Stop!

321
00:21:14,580 --> 00:21:15,659
Don't hide behind your men.

322
00:21:16,219 --> 00:21:17,380
If you've got the guts,

323
00:21:17,380 --> 00:21:18,100
fight me properly.

324
00:21:18,540 --> 00:21:19,060
Fight?

325
00:21:23,739 --> 00:21:25,300
Criminal Investigation Bureau doesn't fight.

326
00:21:26,340 --> 00:21:27,380
We either arrest people

327
00:21:28,820 --> 00:21:29,580
or kill them.

328
00:21:38,340 --> 00:21:38,780
Move.

329
00:21:44,699 --> 00:21:45,620
Don't be rash.

330
00:21:46,699 --> 00:21:48,019
The senior officials stayed quiet.

331
00:21:48,380 --> 00:21:49,340
Why should you jump in?

332
00:21:50,620 --> 00:21:52,100
This is outrageous.

333
00:21:53,580 --> 00:21:54,300
I heard Ye Xian
is a total madman.

334
00:21:55,699 --> 00:21:56,620
He might really

335
00:21:56,699 --> 00:21:58,259
drag you off to prison.

336
00:21:58,540 --> 00:21:59,979
You'd be the one who suffers.

337
00:22:04,219 --> 00:22:04,900
A madman?

338
00:22:08,219 --> 00:22:09,140
Then let's see who is crazier.

339
00:22:16,499 --> 00:22:17,019
What?

340
00:22:18,140 --> 00:22:18,860
Jinzhao

341
00:22:19,380 --> 00:22:21,060
actually beat Lord Chen?

342
00:22:22,060 --> 00:22:23,499
Lord Chen let her win.

343
00:22:24,540 --> 00:22:25,380
You didn't see it.

344
00:22:25,699 --> 00:22:27,300
He'd already won three rounds.

345
00:22:27,459 --> 00:22:29,100
He must've felt awkward.

346
00:22:29,259 --> 00:22:30,100
Starting with Xue Qinglan,
he began going easy.

347
00:22:31,340 --> 00:22:32,620
But who knew Xue Qinglan

348
00:22:32,620 --> 00:22:33,499
wouldn't take it?

349
00:22:33,820 --> 00:22:35,380
She even threw her arrow down

350
00:22:35,580 --> 00:22:36,340
and refused to be let off.

351
00:22:36,459 --> 00:22:37,580
That's how Jinzhao got her turn.

352
00:22:38,179 --> 00:22:39,100
In that case,

353
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:41,820
Jinzhao shouldn't have won.

354
00:22:42,060 --> 00:22:43,419
Look at Xue Qinglan's status.

355
00:22:44,300 --> 00:22:44,820
Even she

356
00:22:45,499 --> 00:22:46,540
was willing to concede.

357
00:22:47,699 --> 00:22:48,979
A girl from our family

358
00:22:49,820 --> 00:22:51,499
should be even more modest.

359
00:22:54,699 --> 00:22:55,459
I heard yesterday
Ye Xian was there too.

360
00:22:56,699 --> 00:22:57,499
And he arrested someone.

361
00:22:57,860 --> 00:22:58,419
Yes, exactly.

362
00:22:58,620 --> 00:22:59,820
Ye Xian suddenly

363
00:22:59,820 --> 00:23:01,179
brought Bureau guards

364
00:23:01,179 --> 00:23:01,979
charging in.

365
00:23:02,380 --> 00:23:02,939
He took

366
00:23:02,939 --> 00:23:04,300
Director Du from Justice

367
00:23:04,340 --> 00:23:05,300
and his family on the spot.

368
00:23:05,820 --> 00:23:07,179
Wenxiu even said

369
00:23:07,459 --> 00:23:09,100
he'd never seen an arrest like that.

370
00:23:09,900 --> 00:23:10,979
I don't know

371
00:23:10,979 --> 00:23:12,259
what's happened to him.

372
00:23:12,739 --> 00:23:14,340
He's like a different person now.

373
00:23:14,780 --> 00:23:16,459
It's honestly a little scary.

374
00:23:17,019 --> 00:23:18,179
What's there to be scared of?

375
00:23:33,620 --> 00:23:34,380
I heard
everyone

376
00:23:34,780 --> 00:23:36,019
was chatting here with Ma'am.

377
00:23:36,380 --> 00:23:37,620
So I came to join in.

378
00:23:38,699 --> 00:23:39,499
Gu Lian,

379
00:23:39,939 --> 00:23:40,780
what were you talking about?

380
00:23:41,140 --> 00:23:42,100
What did Ye Xian do

381
00:23:42,100 --> 00:23:43,179
to scare you so much?

382
00:23:46,179 --> 00:23:47,140
Nothing really.

383
00:23:47,499 --> 00:23:49,340
It was just he

384
00:23:49,340 --> 00:23:50,939
brought Bureau agents

385
00:23:51,340 --> 00:23:52,580
to the spring outing

386
00:23:52,620 --> 00:23:54,540
and arrested Director Du.

387
00:23:55,979 --> 00:23:57,140
I thought it was something serious.

388
00:23:58,019 --> 00:23:59,340
When the Bureau arrests someone,

389
00:23:59,419 --> 00:24:00,380
it's by imperial order.

390
00:24:00,860 --> 00:24:02,060
If His Majesty wants him arrested,

391
00:24:02,219 --> 00:24:03,340
never mind a spring outing,

392
00:24:03,540 --> 00:24:04,499
even at the Luming Banquet,

393
00:24:04,499 --> 00:24:05,659
they still have to take him.

394
00:24:05,900 --> 00:24:07,259
What's the fuss about?

395
00:24:09,820 --> 00:24:10,499
True.

396
00:24:11,939 --> 00:24:13,259
I heard people say

397
00:24:13,499 --> 00:24:15,060
Lord Chief Councilor

398
00:24:15,259 --> 00:24:16,179
meant to match Lord Chen

399
00:24:16,179 --> 00:24:17,499
with Xue Qinglan,

400
00:24:17,540 --> 00:24:18,699
so he held this spring outing.

401
00:24:19,860 --> 00:24:21,699
That's what people are saying.

402
00:24:22,659 --> 00:24:24,459
Then it would be a powerful match.

403
00:24:24,979 --> 00:24:25,540
The Chen family

404
00:24:26,019 --> 00:24:27,659
has served at court for generations.

405
00:24:28,340 --> 00:24:29,140
But the Xue family has been

406
00:24:29,540 --> 00:24:30,580
a top scholar-official clan

407
00:24:30,739 --> 00:24:32,620
since the dynasty began.

408
00:24:33,219 --> 00:24:35,019
They're also His Excellency's in-laws.

409
00:24:35,620 --> 00:24:36,499
In that case,

410
00:24:37,100 --> 00:24:37,659
Lord Chen

411
00:24:37,979 --> 00:24:39,340
is about to climb

412
00:24:39,499 --> 00:24:40,820
is about to climb

413
00:24:43,860 --> 00:24:44,580
Jinzhao.

414
00:24:45,939 --> 00:24:47,499
I heard your grandmother

415
00:24:47,499 --> 00:24:48,780
backed the Chen family

416
00:24:49,100 --> 00:24:50,419
more than ten years ago.

417
00:24:53,060 --> 00:24:54,060
Merchants

418
00:24:54,499 --> 00:24:56,659
are best at betting on the right side.

419
00:24:57,699 --> 00:24:59,340
She did have a good eye.

420
00:25:02,140 --> 00:25:03,179
My grandmother

421
00:25:03,419 --> 00:25:04,459
didn't only bet

422
00:25:04,459 --> 00:25:05,620
on the Chen family.

423
00:25:06,060 --> 00:25:07,259
She also had

424
00:25:07,499 --> 00:25:08,739
high hopes for the Gu family.

425
00:25:09,900 --> 00:25:11,140
That's why she married my mother

426
00:25:11,140 --> 00:25:12,140
into my father's family.

427
00:25:13,620 --> 00:25:14,459
And yet...

428
00:25:16,659 --> 00:25:17,739
Clearly, her judgment

429
00:25:17,860 --> 00:25:18,979
was right sometimes

430
00:25:19,419 --> 00:25:20,380
and wrong sometimes.

431
00:25:22,459 --> 00:25:23,820
In my opinion,

432
00:25:24,179 --> 00:25:25,219
I think

433
00:25:25,380 --> 00:25:26,300
Xue Qinglan

434
00:25:26,300 --> 00:25:27,459
isn't good enough for Chen Yanyun.

435
00:25:27,860 --> 00:25:29,300
She was once engaged.

436
00:25:29,459 --> 00:25:30,659
She's practically a widow.

437
00:25:31,179 --> 00:25:32,459
Chen Yanyun was married, too.

438
00:25:34,300 --> 00:25:35,019
Really?

439
00:25:35,419 --> 00:25:37,459
How is that the same?

440
00:25:37,979 --> 00:25:39,620
If a man was married before,

441
00:25:39,739 --> 00:25:41,019
he can still marry again.

442
00:25:41,540 --> 00:25:43,380
But once a woman is promised,

443
00:25:43,780 --> 00:25:46,060
she's no longer spotless.

444
00:25:47,459 --> 00:25:48,259
Exactly.

445
00:25:49,060 --> 00:25:50,580
Let alone a would-be widow.

446
00:25:50,939 --> 00:25:52,380
Even if a woman is divorced,

447
00:25:53,300 --> 00:25:54,499
people would look down on her

448
00:25:54,860 --> 00:25:56,060
and think her shameful.

449
00:25:56,620 --> 00:25:58,060
Let them look down, then.

450
00:25:58,419 --> 00:26:00,100
The filling isn't in the pleats.

451
00:26:00,419 --> 00:26:01,659
Living well for yourself

452
00:26:01,979 --> 00:26:02,979
is better than saving face

453
00:26:03,259 --> 00:26:04,499
by pretending to be fine

454
00:26:04,620 --> 00:26:05,540
and suffering through it.

455
00:26:17,820 --> 00:26:18,580
Jinzhao.

456
00:26:20,699 --> 00:26:21,459
Auntie.

457
00:26:25,459 --> 00:26:26,979
You're really fired up today.

458
00:26:27,140 --> 00:26:28,659
One word and you snap.

459
00:26:29,380 --> 00:26:30,780
They came at me first.

460
00:26:31,739 --> 00:26:32,860
I can take it if they talk about me.

461
00:26:33,419 --> 00:26:34,939
But they dragged my mother's family in.

462
00:26:36,019 --> 00:26:37,540
Of course I had to hit back.

463
00:26:37,860 --> 00:26:39,060
So they won't try it again.

464
00:26:39,860 --> 00:26:41,499
Aren't you the same, Auntie?

465
00:26:42,140 --> 00:26:42,820
Not the same.

466
00:26:43,659 --> 00:26:44,939
They were talking about Ye Xian.

467
00:26:45,100 --> 00:26:45,979
But no matter how angry I was,

468
00:26:46,219 --> 00:26:46,780
I only dared
take it out on Gu Lian.

469
00:26:48,979 --> 00:26:49,820
Auntie,

470
00:26:49,939 --> 00:26:51,100
you only held back

471
00:26:51,340 --> 00:26:52,540
for Uncle and Hui's sake.

472
00:26:53,019 --> 00:26:54,340
It's not like you're afraid of anyone.

473
00:26:56,300 --> 00:26:58,140
Drop by my courtyard sometime.

474
00:27:09,060 --> 00:27:10,060
That Jinzhao...

475
00:27:10,659 --> 00:27:11,659
Now I see
why Ye Xian

476
00:27:12,300 --> 00:27:13,380
likes her so much.

477
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:15,939
Then...

478
00:27:15,939 --> 00:27:17,259
Why not grant his wish?

479
00:27:19,259 --> 00:27:20,060
No.

480
00:27:21,140 --> 00:27:22,620
The court is suppressing military nobles.

481
00:27:23,100 --> 00:27:23,699
Just look
at how they treat me.

482
00:27:25,219 --> 00:27:26,060
That tells you

483
00:27:26,060 --> 00:27:27,540
how weak the Marquis's is now.

484
00:27:29,140 --> 00:27:30,259
Our only way out

485
00:27:31,179 --> 00:27:33,340
is for Ye Xian to marry well,

486
00:27:33,620 --> 00:27:34,900
then we may still have a chance.

487
00:27:37,179 --> 00:27:38,739
Those snobs are all bastards.

488
00:27:39,179 --> 00:27:40,100
When they asked for my hand,

489
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:41,659
they were so humble.

490
00:27:48,499 --> 00:27:49,259
Miss.

491
00:27:49,499 --> 00:27:50,380
Isn't Mr. Yao
Second Miss's

492
00:27:51,179 --> 00:27:52,219
future husband?

493
00:27:52,860 --> 00:27:54,939
Why would he give you a hairpin?

494
00:27:56,380 --> 00:27:57,499
Yao Wenxiu

495
00:27:58,140 --> 00:27:59,340
is no good.

496
00:28:00,620 --> 00:28:01,140
Then...

497
00:28:01,620 --> 00:28:03,259
Should we tell Second Miss?

498
00:28:03,860 --> 00:28:04,699
Of course not.

499
00:28:05,019 --> 00:28:05,860
What would we say?

500
00:28:06,019 --> 00:28:07,300
That Yao Wenxiu flirted with me?

501
00:28:08,060 --> 00:28:09,459
Things are already

502
00:28:09,739 --> 00:28:10,659
hard enough for me here.

503
00:28:12,979 --> 00:28:14,380
Then this hairpin...

504
00:28:16,939 --> 00:28:17,739
Hide it.

505
00:28:18,060 --> 00:28:18,939
Pretend it never happened.

506
00:28:20,820 --> 00:28:21,820
Okay, Miss.

507
00:28:24,820 --> 00:28:26,419
Sili Hutong was better.

508
00:28:26,820 --> 00:28:28,419
Eldest Miss may be tough,

509
00:28:28,620 --> 00:28:29,459
but she doesn't make trouble.

510
00:28:29,739 --> 00:28:30,699
Not like here.

511
00:28:31,019 --> 00:28:32,259
Second Miss is always...

512
00:28:34,019 --> 00:28:34,820
Enough.

513
00:28:35,499 --> 00:28:36,780
What's the point

514
00:28:37,140 --> 00:28:38,259
of saying that now?

515
00:28:50,219 --> 00:28:51,300
The blisters on feet

516
00:28:51,780 --> 00:28:53,259
came from one's own steps.

517
00:28:54,620 --> 00:28:55,739
From now on,

518
00:28:55,939 --> 00:28:57,100
I can only rely on myself.

519
00:28:59,459 --> 00:29:00,939
Only when I stand firm,

520
00:29:01,780 --> 00:29:03,060
will I have a chance

521
00:29:04,939 --> 00:29:06,060
to bring mother back.

522
00:29:19,499 --> 00:29:20,820
At this spring outing,

523
00:29:21,100 --> 00:29:22,019
the ladies from every family,

524
00:29:22,219 --> 00:29:24,259
old and young alike,

525
00:29:24,739 --> 00:29:26,140
were all trying to stand out.

526
00:29:26,820 --> 00:29:27,499
For one

527
00:29:27,499 --> 00:29:28,699
unique embroidery pattern,

528
00:29:29,060 --> 00:29:30,219
they'd spend a fortune.

529
00:29:30,659 --> 00:29:31,219
So tell me,

530
00:29:31,780 --> 00:29:32,820
what does that mean?

531
00:29:33,380 --> 00:29:34,219
You're right.

532
00:29:35,179 --> 00:29:36,140
The rouge shops

533
00:29:36,259 --> 00:29:37,459
and silk stores this year

534
00:29:37,659 --> 00:29:39,179
are doing over 50% better.

535
00:29:39,739 --> 00:29:40,300
Exactly.

536
00:29:40,540 --> 00:29:41,380
So that means

537
00:29:41,499 --> 00:29:42,900
people have money now.

538
00:29:43,580 --> 00:29:45,380
I plan to turn Linxia House

539
00:29:45,380 --> 00:29:46,820
into a place just for women.

540
00:29:47,259 --> 00:29:48,820
Women can go there

541
00:29:48,820 --> 00:29:50,219
to dine, drink tea,

542
00:29:50,419 --> 00:29:51,380
and watch opera.

543
00:29:51,979 --> 00:29:53,340
Women only.

544
00:29:53,499 --> 00:29:54,900
No men allowed.

545
00:29:55,259 --> 00:29:56,179
Didn't you say

546
00:29:56,179 --> 00:29:57,259
you were going to Shanxi?

547
00:29:57,820 --> 00:29:58,540
Why are you suddenly

548
00:29:58,540 --> 00:29:59,780
focused on business here?

549
00:29:59,979 --> 00:30:01,580
Even if I go to Shanxi,

550
00:30:01,780 --> 00:30:02,780
the business in the capital

551
00:30:02,780 --> 00:30:03,939
can still run as usual.

552
00:30:05,979 --> 00:30:06,620
Alright.

553
00:30:06,939 --> 00:30:07,860
I'll head back first.

554
00:30:14,900 --> 00:30:15,499
Miss.

555
00:30:15,659 --> 00:30:16,739
Have you made up your mind

556
00:30:16,739 --> 00:30:17,699
not to go to Shanxi?

557
00:30:18,219 --> 00:30:19,179
Not yet.

558
00:30:19,419 --> 00:30:20,540
I just feel better

559
00:30:20,860 --> 00:30:21,780
having both plans ready.

560
00:30:22,459 --> 00:30:23,300
Linxia House

561
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:24,820
is half a fallback for me.

562
00:30:25,259 --> 00:30:25,979
Miss Gu.

563
00:30:28,459 --> 00:30:29,699
You are...?

564
00:30:32,900 --> 00:30:34,219
I'm Wang Zan.

565
00:30:35,459 --> 00:30:37,860
My father heads the Dali...

566
00:30:38,140 --> 00:30:38,739
Court.

567
00:30:39,380 --> 00:30:40,540
Greetings, Mr. Wang.

568
00:30:41,580 --> 00:30:43,820
What brings you here?

569
00:30:44,219 --> 00:30:45,219
Yesterday at the match,

570
00:30:45,580 --> 00:30:46,900
it was almost my turn,

571
00:30:46,979 --> 00:30:48,060
but then Ye Xian

572
00:30:48,060 --> 00:30:48,979
ruined it.

573
00:30:49,340 --> 00:30:51,060
I couldn't sleep all night.

574
00:30:51,739 --> 00:30:52,620
And today,

575
00:30:52,620 --> 00:30:53,860
I met you as soon as I went out.

576
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:55,499
Seems my wish came true.

577
00:30:56,140 --> 00:30:56,979
I have an estate.

578
00:30:57,060 --> 00:30:58,259
It has a training field ready.

579
00:30:58,580 --> 00:31:00,019
No time like today.

580
00:31:00,259 --> 00:31:01,900
Let's go have a match.

581
00:31:02,100 --> 00:31:03,580
You must be joking, Mr. Wang.

582
00:31:04,019 --> 00:31:04,939
I have things to do,
I should go.

583
00:31:05,939 --> 00:31:06,659
Don't go.

584
00:31:07,019 --> 00:31:07,900
You're just a young lady.
What could be so urgent?

585
00:31:09,140 --> 00:31:09,820
Just one match.

586
00:31:10,219 --> 00:31:11,300
I won't feel right if we don't.

587
00:31:11,860 --> 00:31:14,179
If you really want a match,

588
00:31:14,419 --> 00:31:15,699
wait for the next spring outing.

589
00:31:15,699 --> 00:31:16,179
The...

590
00:31:16,699 --> 00:31:18,179
The next spring outing?

591
00:31:18,179 --> 00:31:19,419
That's not until next year.

592
00:31:19,620 --> 00:31:20,100
No way.

593
00:31:22,340 --> 00:31:23,860
You don't want to compete, do you?

594
00:31:24,419 --> 00:31:25,659
That's fine. How about this?

595
00:31:26,300 --> 00:31:27,219
I'll treat you to a meal.

596
00:31:27,459 --> 00:31:28,340
At Linxia House.

597
00:31:28,340 --> 00:31:29,620
Their best feast.

598
00:31:30,219 --> 00:31:30,939
Come on.

599
00:31:31,019 --> 00:31:31,979
Do me this favor.
Show some respect.

600
00:31:33,140 --> 00:31:33,820
Who're you, girl?
Move.

601
00:31:34,780 --> 00:31:35,620
Come on.

602
00:31:36,419 --> 00:31:37,259
What're you doing?

603
00:31:38,860 --> 00:31:39,380
What?

604
00:31:40,100 --> 00:31:40,900
Won't give me face?

605
00:31:41,340 --> 00:31:42,459
I came to you sincerely

606
00:31:42,459 --> 00:31:43,340
to make friends.

607
00:31:43,459 --> 00:31:44,580
Don't throw my kindness back at me.

608
00:31:47,140 --> 00:31:47,979
I get it.

609
00:31:48,499 --> 00:31:49,739
You look down on me.

610
00:31:49,860 --> 00:31:50,699
Makes sense.

611
00:31:51,459 --> 00:31:53,179
Girls like you nowadays

612
00:31:54,100 --> 00:31:55,860
only care for pretty boys.

613
00:31:56,259 --> 00:31:56,860
What?

614
00:31:57,259 --> 00:31:58,140
Who have you got your eye on?

615
00:31:58,939 --> 00:32:01,300
Don't tell me it's Yao Wenxiu.

616
00:32:02,540 --> 00:32:03,659
Are you out of your mind?

617
00:32:06,340 --> 00:32:07,699
Why are you always around?

618
00:32:09,939 --> 00:32:11,259
Miss, just go.

619
00:32:11,620 --> 00:32:12,259
I'll handle this.

620
00:32:13,459 --> 00:32:14,300
Easy! That hurts!

621
00:32:15,659 --> 00:32:16,699
Move aside.

622
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:21,900
Gu Jinzhao!

623
00:32:22,580 --> 00:32:23,659
You'll pay for this!

624
00:32:26,100 --> 00:32:27,100
Grand Tutor Xue

625
00:32:27,100 --> 00:32:28,540
came in person yesterday.

626
00:32:28,939 --> 00:32:30,219
He said Qinglan's temper

627
00:32:30,219 --> 00:32:31,219
is quite different from yours.

628
00:32:31,699 --> 00:32:33,499
He fears you may not get along.

629
00:32:34,019 --> 00:32:35,140
You needn't worry, Ma'am.

630
00:32:35,860 --> 00:32:36,939
Families meet for marriage talks.

631
00:32:37,140 --> 00:32:38,499
It doesn't always work out.

632
00:32:38,860 --> 00:32:39,699
Besides,

633
00:32:40,060 --> 00:32:41,540
I'm a few years older than Miss Xue

634
00:32:42,060 --> 00:32:42,939
and have been married before.

635
00:32:43,620 --> 00:32:45,340
I truly don't deserve her.

636
00:32:51,419 --> 00:32:52,780
Qinglan was once

637
00:32:53,340 --> 00:32:54,540
promised to someone, too.

638
00:32:55,060 --> 00:32:56,140
Before she could marry him,

639
00:32:56,140 --> 00:32:57,699
the man fell ill and died.

640
00:32:58,900 --> 00:33:00,019
Lord Xue has always felt

641
00:33:00,019 --> 00:33:01,060
he failed his daughter.

642
00:33:01,259 --> 00:33:03,620
So he gives in to her in everything.

643
00:33:03,620 --> 00:33:04,780
And now,

644
00:33:05,580 --> 00:33:06,979
no one can rein her in.

645
00:33:08,739 --> 00:33:10,019
In my view,

646
00:33:11,179 --> 00:33:12,459
she's been spoiled.

647
00:33:14,380 --> 00:33:15,060
Later,

648
00:33:15,060 --> 00:33:16,540
I'll look around carefully for you,

649
00:33:16,780 --> 00:33:17,820
and find someone better.

650
00:33:21,300 --> 00:33:22,179
Thank you, Ma'am.

651
00:33:23,300 --> 00:33:24,499
At first, I only thought

652
00:33:24,499 --> 00:33:26,060
Qinglan, in both family

653
00:33:26,380 --> 00:33:27,419
and status, suited you well.

654
00:33:27,860 --> 00:33:29,179
I overlooked the rest.

655
00:33:30,459 --> 00:33:31,780
I never asked you

656
00:33:31,939 --> 00:33:33,300
what kind of woman you want.

657
00:33:35,540 --> 00:33:36,780
To be honest, Ma'am,

658
00:33:37,540 --> 00:33:38,860
after Jiang passed away,

659
00:33:39,100 --> 00:33:40,179
all these years,

660
00:33:40,380 --> 00:33:41,659
I have long

661
00:33:41,820 --> 00:33:43,820
stopped expecting much from marriage.

662
00:33:44,219 --> 00:33:45,659
If I must remarry,

663
00:33:45,979 --> 00:33:48,060
I only hope she's reasonable,

664
00:33:48,259 --> 00:33:49,979
smart, and sensible.

665
00:33:59,860 --> 00:34:01,259
I'll take my leave.

666
00:34:11,019 --> 00:34:12,660
Look at Jiuheng.

667
00:34:12,979 --> 00:34:14,499
He seems truly disheartened.

668
00:34:17,059 --> 00:34:18,700
You actually believe him?

669
00:34:19,340 --> 00:34:19,979
What do you mean?

670
00:34:21,700 --> 00:34:23,619
He never wanted this match

671
00:34:23,619 --> 00:34:25,260
from the very start.

672
00:34:26,099 --> 00:34:28,019
He only played along

673
00:34:28,340 --> 00:34:29,539
because we pushed for it.

674
00:34:30,220 --> 00:34:32,099
But at the spring outing,

675
00:34:32,340 --> 00:34:33,660
he went easy on Qinglan

676
00:34:34,019 --> 00:34:35,579
just to make her angry

677
00:34:35,740 --> 00:34:37,099
and make her say herself

678
00:34:37,099 --> 00:34:39,019
that the match wasn't right.

679
00:34:39,780 --> 00:34:40,979
And what he just said

680
00:34:40,979 --> 00:34:41,979
about wanting someone

681
00:34:42,380 --> 00:34:44,180
gentle and virtuous,

682
00:34:44,579 --> 00:34:46,260
sensible and understanding...

683
00:34:46,619 --> 00:34:47,820
He was really saying

684
00:34:48,019 --> 00:34:49,220
we were wrong

685
00:34:49,340 --> 00:34:50,459
to choose Qinglan for him.

686
00:34:53,740 --> 00:34:54,419
He really has

687
00:34:54,419 --> 00:34:55,619
too many tricks up his sleeve.

688
00:35:02,900 --> 00:35:04,419
You want to buy into my business?

689
00:35:10,820 --> 00:35:12,059
This is the money

690
00:35:12,059 --> 00:35:13,260
I've saved over the years.

691
00:35:14,260 --> 00:35:15,180
I counted it.

692
00:35:15,499 --> 00:35:16,820
It's 8,000 taels in total.

693
00:35:17,939 --> 00:35:18,780
You can have it all.

694
00:35:20,459 --> 00:35:21,539
8,000 taels

695
00:35:21,740 --> 00:35:22,700
is already a lot.

696
00:35:23,180 --> 00:35:23,820
It's not enough.

697
00:35:24,579 --> 00:35:26,099
When Second Sister marries Yao Wenxiu,

698
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:28,139
her dowry silver alone is 20,000 taels.

699
00:35:28,979 --> 00:35:30,499
Though somehow later

700
00:35:30,619 --> 00:35:31,660
it became 2,000 taels.

701
00:35:32,139 --> 00:35:33,419
But that shows

702
00:35:33,419 --> 00:35:34,459
what marriages cost in the capital.

703
00:35:34,939 --> 00:35:35,780
8,000 taels

704
00:35:36,380 --> 00:35:37,300
won't get me far.

705
00:35:39,820 --> 00:35:42,539
You want to earn your own dowry?

706
00:35:44,700 --> 00:35:45,340
Yes.

707
00:35:46,660 --> 00:35:48,499
My mother is still suffering in the temple.

708
00:35:48,900 --> 00:35:50,459
And father is the way he is.

709
00:35:51,740 --> 00:35:53,419
I have to find my own way.

710
00:35:54,419 --> 00:35:55,700
Can you help me?

711
00:35:55,860 --> 00:35:56,860
Let me take a share
in your business.

712
00:35:58,459 --> 00:35:59,539
I don't care what trade it is.

713
00:35:59,740 --> 00:36:00,419
I'm not greedy either.

714
00:36:00,700 --> 00:36:01,860
As long as it makes money.

715
00:36:05,419 --> 00:36:06,059
No.

716
00:36:12,019 --> 00:36:13,220
Is the money not enough?

717
00:36:13,939 --> 00:36:14,780
I'll scrape together more.

718
00:36:16,260 --> 00:36:17,419
It's not about the money.

719
00:36:18,059 --> 00:36:19,260
No matter how much you offer,

720
00:36:19,459 --> 00:36:20,619
I won't say yes.

721
00:36:21,539 --> 00:36:22,300
Go back.

722
00:36:24,380 --> 00:36:25,220
Why?

723
00:36:29,340 --> 00:36:30,099
Jinzhao.

724
00:36:30,860 --> 00:36:32,260
I know you don't like me.

725
00:36:32,860 --> 00:36:33,900
But

726
00:36:34,099 --> 00:36:35,619
we're still sisters.

727
00:36:36,700 --> 00:36:37,740
Please help me.

728
00:36:38,019 --> 00:36:39,099
Let me take a share

729
00:36:39,099 --> 00:36:40,019
in your business.

730
00:36:41,220 --> 00:36:42,300
What if it loses money?

731
00:36:44,539 --> 00:36:45,499
Business

732
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:47,499
can lose money, too.

733
00:36:48,180 --> 00:36:49,300
You just said

734
00:36:49,300 --> 00:36:50,180
you weren't greedy,

735
00:36:50,539 --> 00:36:51,780
that any profit would do.

736
00:36:52,780 --> 00:36:54,059
That sentence alone

737
00:36:54,539 --> 00:36:55,419
is enough for me
to turn you down.

738
00:37:00,300 --> 00:37:01,220
Sit down first.

739
00:37:07,539 --> 00:37:09,139
I know what you're thinking.

740
00:37:10,180 --> 00:37:11,380
You have no real income,

741
00:37:11,979 --> 00:37:13,579
and the money you have

742
00:37:13,780 --> 00:37:14,419
isn't much.

743
00:37:15,139 --> 00:37:17,340
So you don't dare take risks.

744
00:37:19,099 --> 00:37:20,660
But I never work with people

745
00:37:21,380 --> 00:37:22,979
who are afraid of risk.

746
00:37:29,740 --> 00:37:30,740
Qing is here.

747
00:37:33,900 --> 00:37:36,459
Grandmother. Uncle. Auntie.

748
00:37:37,099 --> 00:37:38,740
You're back. Sit down.

749
00:37:43,019 --> 00:37:43,900
Are you off today?

750
00:37:44,700 --> 00:37:45,180
Yes.

751
00:37:45,619 --> 00:37:47,300
I came back for some books.

752
00:37:47,780 --> 00:37:49,260
You haven't eaten, have you?

753
00:37:49,740 --> 00:37:50,419
Not yet.

754
00:37:50,939 --> 00:37:51,740
On the way here,

755
00:37:51,900 --> 00:37:53,180
I was hoping to get a bite here.

756
00:37:54,939 --> 00:37:55,459
Hurry.

757
00:37:55,700 --> 00:37:56,820
Bring over

758
00:37:56,820 --> 00:37:58,260
the fresh meat-filled qizi shaobing

759
00:37:58,260 --> 00:37:59,180
on a plate.

760
00:37:59,660 --> 00:38:01,139
Qing loves those.

761
00:38:01,340 --> 00:38:01,979
Okay.

762
00:38:02,139 --> 00:38:03,059
Thank you, Grandmother.

763
00:38:03,300 --> 00:38:04,099
You're the best.

764
00:38:04,499 --> 00:38:05,539
So, our young Tanhua,

765
00:38:05,939 --> 00:38:07,220
after a few days in office,

766
00:38:07,419 --> 00:38:08,700
you've learned to sweet-talk us.

767
00:38:09,180 --> 00:38:10,340
You're teasing me, Auntie.

768
00:38:11,939 --> 00:38:13,459
Good timing.

769
00:38:14,380 --> 00:38:15,099
I was just about

770
00:38:15,099 --> 00:38:16,860
to discuss it with your uncle.

771
00:38:17,180 --> 00:38:19,700
Your job is settled now.

772
00:38:20,139 --> 00:38:22,419
Your marriage to Wanxue

773
00:38:22,740 --> 00:38:24,180
should be prepared, too.

774
00:38:24,579 --> 00:38:26,740
How about the end of the year?

775
00:38:27,579 --> 00:38:28,499
The end of the year?

776
00:38:29,059 --> 00:38:30,300
That may be a little tight.

777
00:38:33,059 --> 00:38:33,780
Well...

778
00:38:34,220 --> 00:38:35,459
The court is sending envoys

779
00:38:35,459 --> 00:38:36,579
for peace talks with Beiman.

780
00:38:37,300 --> 00:38:38,539
The Hanlin Academy has to send someone, too.

781
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:40,380
Today, I asked Scholar Chang

782
00:38:40,380 --> 00:38:41,220
to recommend me for it.

783
00:38:41,700 --> 00:38:43,579
He said if you agree,

784
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:44,740
he won't stop me.

785
00:38:46,139 --> 00:38:47,220
You want to go to Beiman?

786
00:38:48,139 --> 00:38:50,139
It's dangerous.

787
00:38:50,660 --> 00:38:52,220
Why would you go there?

788
00:38:53,180 --> 00:38:54,139
Don't worry, Grandmother.

789
00:38:54,300 --> 00:38:55,979
Beiman's envoys are coming here.

790
00:38:56,419 --> 00:38:57,380
Our envoys

791
00:38:57,380 --> 00:38:58,499
only need to go to Datong.

792
00:39:03,660 --> 00:39:05,059
Why the sudden interest

793
00:39:05,380 --> 00:39:06,660
in getting involved?

794
00:39:07,419 --> 00:39:08,499
Are you unhappy

795
00:39:08,499 --> 00:39:09,579
at the Hanlin Academy?

796
00:39:09,780 --> 00:39:10,820
To be honest, Uncle,

797
00:39:11,220 --> 00:39:11,939
at the Hanlin Academy,

798
00:39:12,019 --> 00:39:13,180
I'm not unhappy.

799
00:39:13,340 --> 00:39:14,300
It's too comfortable.

800
00:39:14,939 --> 00:39:16,059
I only edit official texts each day.

801
00:39:16,059 --> 00:39:17,059
And not even much.

802
00:39:17,459 --> 00:39:18,180
If I do too much,

803
00:39:18,180 --> 00:39:19,419
my colleagues get uncomfortable.

804
00:39:19,780 --> 00:39:20,740
Five entries a day
is enough for my superior.

805
00:39:22,380 --> 00:39:23,860
The rest is just reading,

806
00:39:23,979 --> 00:39:24,660
and writing a little.

807
00:39:25,059 --> 00:39:25,979
Because of you,

808
00:39:26,380 --> 00:39:27,340
everyone treats me

809
00:39:27,340 --> 00:39:28,459
with great courtesy.

810
00:39:29,419 --> 00:39:30,619
I'm afraid if I drift along

811
00:39:30,619 --> 00:39:31,499
like this for a few years,

812
00:39:31,700 --> 00:39:32,860
I'll lose my edge.

813
00:39:34,740 --> 00:39:35,499
Impatient?

814
00:39:36,939 --> 00:39:37,539
Yes.

815
00:39:38,579 --> 00:39:39,180
Back then,

816
00:39:39,260 --> 00:39:40,660
you also left the Hanlin Academy

817
00:39:40,660 --> 00:39:41,660
for the Canal Transport Office.

818
00:39:42,499 --> 00:39:44,619
I want to follow your example

819
00:39:44,979 --> 00:39:45,619
and hope

820
00:39:45,619 --> 00:39:47,139
to do some real work.

821
00:39:49,459 --> 00:39:51,099
This peace talk with Beiman

822
00:39:51,700 --> 00:39:53,340
matters a great deal to the court.

823
00:39:54,740 --> 00:39:55,939
If you go well,

824
00:39:56,619 --> 00:39:57,860
that will be no small merit.

825
00:39:58,860 --> 00:40:00,099
And you're a first-rank graduate.

826
00:40:00,700 --> 00:40:01,419
When you return,

827
00:40:01,900 --> 00:40:03,180
the court will surely use you well.

828
00:40:03,860 --> 00:40:04,860
That is faster

829
00:40:04,939 --> 00:40:06,220
than staying in Hanlin Academy,

830
00:40:06,220 --> 00:40:07,180
slowly working your way up

831
00:40:07,380 --> 00:40:08,619
and waiting for promotion.

832
00:40:10,539 --> 00:40:11,660
Since you've thought it through,

833
00:40:12,139 --> 00:40:12,900
go, then.

834
00:40:18,260 --> 00:40:19,499
Thank you, Uncle.

835
00:40:20,820 --> 00:40:21,300
Sit.

836
00:40:25,539 --> 00:40:26,860
A trip to Datong

837
00:40:27,180 --> 00:40:28,700
will take months both ways.

838
00:40:29,099 --> 00:40:30,220
Your marriage to Wanxue

839
00:40:30,220 --> 00:40:31,300
may have to be delayed again.

840
00:40:33,059 --> 00:40:34,539
Then let it wait.

841
00:40:35,260 --> 00:40:36,939
His future matters more.

842
00:40:41,099 --> 00:40:43,419
Now she regrets sending him after rank.

843
00:40:44,459 --> 00:40:45,220
Be quiet.

844
00:40:48,380 --> 00:40:48,979
Drink your soup.

845
00:40:51,780 --> 00:40:52,539
Smells good.

846
00:41:12,380 --> 00:41:14,260
Inside is a Duan inkstone

847
00:41:14,380 --> 00:41:15,380
and a box of Umbral Ink.

848
00:41:15,820 --> 00:41:17,059
The ink is nothing special,

849
00:41:17,380 --> 00:41:18,459
but this inkstone

850
00:41:18,900 --> 00:41:20,300
is an antique from the old dynasty.

851
00:41:23,099 --> 00:41:24,860
I found it simple and charming,

852
00:41:25,220 --> 00:41:26,780
so I brought it for you today.

853
00:41:40,860 --> 00:41:42,780
Hearing the wedding won't be this year

854
00:41:42,900 --> 00:41:44,099
has brightened you right up.

855
00:41:44,900 --> 00:41:45,700
You talk too much.

856
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:47,740
I know, actually.

857
00:41:48,059 --> 00:41:49,260
If it weren't Miss Yu,

858
00:41:49,300 --> 00:41:50,380
but Miss Gu instead,

859
00:41:50,579 --> 00:41:52,220
you wouldn't go to Shanxi.

860
00:41:53,019 --> 00:41:53,660
Yunting.

861
00:41:54,099 --> 00:41:55,019
If I ever

862
00:41:55,499 --> 00:41:57,260
hear you say that again,

863
00:41:58,499 --> 00:41:59,939
you won't serve me anymore.

864
00:42:01,780 --> 00:42:02,660
I understand.

865
00:42:03,019 --> 00:42:04,099
I won't say it again.

866
00:42:20,459 --> 00:42:20,979
Sir.

867
00:42:21,260 --> 00:42:22,459
She's from the Xue family.

868
00:42:22,619 --> 00:42:23,499
She brought you an invitation.

869
00:42:23,660 --> 00:42:24,939
She's waited since afternoon.

870
00:42:26,539 --> 00:42:27,340
Which Xue family?

871
00:42:34,220 --> 00:42:35,260
Xue Qinglan.

872
00:42:35,499 --> 00:42:36,139
My lady

873
00:42:36,139 --> 00:42:37,700
asks when Your Lordship is free.

874
00:42:38,139 --> 00:42:39,740
She'd like to treat you at Linxia House.

875
00:42:39,939 --> 00:42:41,019
Treat me?

876
00:42:45,459 --> 00:42:46,499
Lord Ye said

877
00:42:46,740 --> 00:42:47,900
he's busy with work lately

878
00:42:48,099 --> 00:42:49,220
and can't spare the time.

879
00:42:53,380 --> 00:42:54,340
I want his exact words.

880
00:42:56,380 --> 00:42:57,660
His exact words were...

881
00:42:58,220 --> 00:42:59,459
"Nothing better to do?"

882
00:42:59,820 --> 00:43:00,860
"Go sit somewhere else."

883
00:43:09,099 --> 00:43:10,059
Interesting.

884
00:43:10,860 --> 00:43:11,740
It's been a long time

885
00:43:11,740 --> 00:43:12,939
since I met someone this fun.

886
00:43:20,860 --> 00:43:22,939
Did she say she had no time for me?

887
00:43:23,619 --> 00:43:25,260
Qingpu relayed the message.

888
00:43:25,459 --> 00:43:26,260
Miss Gu must

889
00:43:26,260 --> 00:43:27,419
be busy with business,

890
00:43:27,419 --> 00:43:28,220
so...

891
00:43:30,340 --> 00:43:31,979
She's still mad at me

892
00:43:32,019 --> 00:43:32,820
over the spring outing.

893
00:43:36,380 --> 00:43:37,019
By the way, Sir.

894
00:43:37,419 --> 00:43:38,740
I heard a rumor.

895
00:43:39,019 --> 00:43:40,499
The Wang family

896
00:43:40,740 --> 00:43:41,820
has their eye on Miss Gu.

897
00:43:42,220 --> 00:43:43,740
Wang Shenzhi's son?

898
00:43:43,740 --> 00:43:44,260
Wang Zan?

899
00:43:44,780 --> 00:43:45,220
Yes.

900
00:43:45,820 --> 00:43:46,579
Mr. Wang

901
00:43:46,579 --> 00:43:47,860
has been telling everyone

902
00:43:48,499 --> 00:43:49,979
that Miss Gu is unruly,

903
00:43:50,340 --> 00:43:51,539
and if his grandmother

904
00:43:51,539 --> 00:43:53,059
didn't know Madam Ji,

905
00:43:53,380 --> 00:43:54,660
he wouldn't even consider her.

906
00:43:55,139 --> 00:43:56,419
From what I heard,

907
00:43:56,539 --> 00:43:58,180
it sounds like a proposal is coming.

908
00:43:58,939 --> 00:44:00,260
A man like Wang Zan...

909
00:44:00,579 --> 00:44:01,459
As if he's worthy.

910
00:44:01,860 --> 00:44:02,539
Exactly.

911
00:44:03,660 --> 00:44:04,260
Lord.

912
00:44:04,900 --> 00:44:06,660
We can't let them propose, can we?

913
00:44:06,820 --> 00:44:07,459
Of course not.
